        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】Realme 推出可拆换镜头概念智能电话，一吋 sensor、人像长焦兼备</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/realme-ultra/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=realme-ultra</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/realme-ultra/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 11:18:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MWC2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[realme Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295212</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>随著科技不断进步，智慧型手机摄影迎来新里程碑。realme 在 2025 年世界流动通信大会（MWC 2025）上，首次展示其可拆换镜头概念机。这款创新产品配备 1 吋 Sony 订制感光元件及独特镜头接口设计，让用户可直接安装专业单眼镜头，革新手机拍摄体验。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295230" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370544-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370544-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370544.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配备一吋 Sensor</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295231" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370559-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370559-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370559.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这款概念机名为 ULTRA，内置 1 吋影像感测器，并配备两款专业镜头：73mm 人像镜头及 234mm 长焦镜头，实现 10 倍光学变焦。从官方影片可见，产品包装盒分为手机与镜头两部分，设计新颖。其光学画质媲美单眼相机，无论细腻景深或远距离拍摄，均令人耳目一新。据 IT 之家报导，realme 强调这是品牌首款支援 10 倍光学变焦的机型，技术突破备受瞩目。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370531-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370531-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370531.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371032-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371032-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371032.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295233" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371044-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371044-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371044.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295234" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371054-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371054-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371054.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>消息一出，立即引起网民热议。X 用户 Shindensha 表示：「realme 这款机感觉真系可以随需装镜头，相当有趣，没想到这种手机会出自 realme。」</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">realmeのやつ、なんか本当に交换式というか、交换式というよりはレンズが付属していて、必要に応じて取付できる感じに见えるな<br />
ええめっちゃ面白いと思うけど、こういうスマホがrealmeから出ることが冲撃ですよ。</p><p>— はるつばめ (@Shindensha) <a href="https://twitter.com/Shindensha/status/1894735203337445598?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 26, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br />
另有网民 MItu8_san 则关注技术细节：「如果是 1 吋感测器加可换镜头，手机厚度会否成问题？」此外小米早于 2022 年推出 12S Ultra 概念机，支援 Leica M 系列镜头；而今年小米再推磁吸式模组光学系统，显示手机摄影技术竞争日趋激烈。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">Realme Ultraがレンズ交换式って初出どこなん&#8230;？<br />
ティザー画像から类推するに中央の洼みは単なるペリスコープでもし1インチセンサーならイヤでもテレセントリック性悪化するでしょ<br />
それかフランジバック分稼いでるにしてもスマホの筐体じゃねえ</p><p>— みつば (@MItu8_san) <a href="https://twitter.com/MItu8_san/status/1895689309132636663?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 1, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>realme 凭借可拆换镜头概念机及 14 Pro 系列，在 MWC 2025 上展现技术实力与市场野心。这款手机若顺利推出市场，可能掀起手机摄影新浪潮。</p><p>资料来源：IT 之家</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
