        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】小米研发磁吸 M4/3 镜头模组，1 亿像素、等效 35 mm f/1.4</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/xiaomi-unveils-ambitious-modular-phone-concept-with-lens-attachment/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xiaomi-unveils-ambitious-modular-phone-concept-with-lens-attachment</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/xiaomi-unveils-ambitious-modular-phone-concept-with-lens-attachment/mobile-phone/phone-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:59:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手机配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[m43]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MWC2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米模块光学系统]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295203</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米于 2025 年 MWC 世界移动通讯大会上展示了一项全新概念产品——「小米模块光学系统」，系统透过磁吸式设计，将配备 1 亿像素 M4/3 感光器及 35mm f/1.4 定焦镜头的模组与手机连接，提升手机摄影画质及功能。该技术利用高速触点传输影像数据，实现相机光学与手机计算能力的深度结合。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/f91feba0f7fd11efb7ff-694x365.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/f91feba0f7fd11efb7ff-694x365.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/f91feba0f7fd11efb7ff.jpeg 959w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295208" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295209" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「小米模块光学系统」采用磁吸触点技术，模组内置 1 亿像素 M4/3 感光器及 f/1.4 大光圈定焦镜头，支援 RAW 格式拍摄，并配备自动对焦马达及手动对焦环。据外媒报导，该系统使用小米独有的 LaserLink 技术，数据传输速度极快，与手机内置相机体验相近。产品设计灵感或源于 Sony QX 系列及 Motorola Moto Mods，但小米在稳定性及画质上作出显著改进。X 网民 real_veryjack 表示：「M43 画幅加 f1.4 光圈，体积小巧，对爱好轻便设备的人来说吸引力很大。」</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="zh">小米最近公布的一个概念产品 &#8212; 外挂镜头，真的是太吸引我了🤩。M43 画幅，f1.4 的光圈（相当于全画幅的 f2.8），等效 35mm 焦段📷。体积只有一个饼干镜头大小，比口袋里塞一个卡片机还要方便。对于喜欢小巧产品的人来说，根本把持不住，期待产品落地。<a href="https://t.co/QSzO1gPpMm">https://t.co/QSzO1gPpMm</a></p><p>— 阿杰 Jack (@real_veryjack) <a href="https://twitter.com/real_veryjack/status/1896469508237447503?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 3, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>回顾过去，Sony 于 2013 年推出 QX 系列镜头相机，虽有 1 寸感光器及 10X 光学变焦，但因 Wi-Fi 连线不稳而失败。2016 年 Motorola 与 Hasselblad 合作的 Moto Mods True Zoom 则配备 1/2.3 寸感光器及氙气闪灯，却因画质提升有限未获成功。小米的方案则以更大感光器及触点传输技术，试图突破瓶颈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>小米这款概念产品展现了手机摄影的新可能性，未来的发展或取决于市场反馈及技术成熟度。若成功量产，或许能开创手机外接光学模组的新生态，改变消费者对手机摄影的认知。业界预测小米于后续发布会透露更多计划。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_97130"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BBuvc_K8tDg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://www.androidauthority.com/xiaomi-concept-modular-phone-attachable-lens-3531335/">Android Authority</a>、<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E9%A0%90%E7%A0%94%E7%A3%81%E5%90%B8-m43-%E5%AE%9A%E7%84%A6%E6%A8%A1%E7%B5%84%E5%85%89%E5%AD%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%87%E7%9B%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%85%89%E5%AD%B8%E8%88%87%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%AE%97%E5%8A%9B%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88%E3%80%8D-071605623.html">Yahoo</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
