        <item>
            <title>一啪上电脑即变三屏幕   Lenovo Magic Bay Dual Display 模组化概念配件发表</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/lenovo-magic-bay-dual-display/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-magic-bay-dual-display</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/lenovo-magic-bay-dual-display/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 08:55:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lenovo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Magic Bay Dual Display]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295188</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p data-start="40" data-end="160">Lenovo 于 2025 年世界流动通讯大会（MWC 2025）正式发表一款崭新模组化概念，让笔电透过 Magic Bay 生态系统扩充成三屏幕便携式工作站。这个产品针对专业用户，为经常需要处理多任务的商务人士提供更高效的工作体验。</p><p data-start="40" data-end="160"><h3 data-start="162" data-end="195"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vj4qslplhuf9rlbjtesb-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vj4qslplhuf9rlbjtesb-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vj4qslplhuf9rlbjtesb.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3 data-start="162" data-end="195"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02958jpg-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02958jpg-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02958jpg.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p data-start="196" data-end="363">Lenovo 于 ThinkBook 16p Gen 6 笔电上推出 Magic Bay 系列模组化配件。其中 <strong data-start="262" data-end="291">Magic Bay Dual Display 概念产品</strong> 让用户能额外添加两块 13.3 吋副屏幕，变成一个完整的三屏幕工作站，提升数据视觉化、内容编辑及协作效率，无需外接传统显示器即可实现多工处理。</p><p data-start="196" data-end="363"><p data-start="365" data-end="497">除了三屏幕配置，Lenovo 亦展示 <strong data-start="384" data-end="412">Magic Bay 2nd Display 概念</strong>，这是一款 8 吋小型副屏幕，可作为 AI 仪表板，提供即时存取生产力工具、讯息应用程式及 AI 生成数据分析，确保用户随时掌握关键资讯，特别适合需要灵活工作的专业人士。</p><p data-start="365" data-end="497"><p data-start="521" data-end="676">Lenovo 于 MWC 2025 前夕率先展示该技术，Magic Bay Dual Display 概念让笔电能够透过磁吸式基座扩展为三屏幕配置，当用户将副屏幕安装于 ThinkBook 16p Gen 6，系统会自动识别，无需额外设置即可运行。此设计简化了以往笔电使用多屏幕的繁琐步骤，让移动办公更具弹性。</p><p data-start="521" data-end="676"><h3 data-start="162" data-end="195"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ek1h64dscf2784jpg-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ek1h64dscf2784jpg-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ek1h64dscf2784jpg.jpg 829w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p data-start="521" data-end="676"><p data-start="678" data-end="797">根据《Laptop Mag》预览报导，这套显示技术运作流畅，屏幕可折叠收纳于笔电背部，使用时迅速展开并立即连接。对于经常携带设备出差的专业人士，这种便携式三屏幕设计能够大幅提升工作效率，无论是处理数据、视讯会议还是内容编辑，皆能流畅运行。</p><p data-start="678" data-end="797"><p data-start="825" data-end="956">资料来源：<a href="https://news.lenovo.com/pressroom/press-releases/advancing-ai-powered-business-computing-thinkpad-thinkbook-concept-devices/">Lenovo</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
